WEBVTT

00:01.039 --> 00:02.539
Why are you here?

00:02.539 --> 00:03.939
It wasn't the rapture!

00:03.939 --> 00:06.139
They were no better than us! I have proof!

00:06.139 --> 00:08.639
Free of charge!

00:08.639 --> 00:10.639
She beat her children!

00:10.639 --> 00:12.339
It was not the rapture!

00:12.339 --> 00:13.339
Matt.

00:13.339 --> 00:14.539
Really need to do this today?

00:14.539 --> 00:15.539
Especially today.

00:15.539 --> 00:17.039
Next time you see your dad,

00:17.039 --> 00:18.639
you tell him he's off the hook.

00:18.639 --> 00:19.839
I will be sure and do that, Matt.

00:19.839 --> 00:22.839
I'm not asking for that
perfect day at the beach.

00:22.839 --> 00:26.239
Just give me all four of
us alive and together.

00:26.239 --> 00:28.239
A year ago, these people didn't even exist.

00:28.239 --> 00:30.239
Now there's almost 50 of them.

00:30.239 --> 00:31.239
Where did they come from?

00:31.239 --> 00:32.238
What do they want?

00:32.238 --> 00:33.839
You don't even know who they are.

00:33.839 --> 00:35.339
We know who they were.

00:35.339 --> 00:37.339
I'm trying to talk to my wife!

00:37.339 --> 00:38.739
Please come home.

00:39.356 --> 00:41.956
Do you even remember what it
feels like to care about anything?

00:41.956 --> 00:43.756
_

